Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.40,0:00:05.48,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Richie. I'm sorry for lyin' to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.11,0:00:08.60,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Be good to Ri'ko.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.47,0:00:10.35,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Take care.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.21,0:00:16.51,Songs,,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.51,0:00:22.00,Songs,,0000,0000,0000,,I forget what I was like before I met you
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.36,0:00:26.41,Songs,,0000,0000,0000,,The wind caresses my cheek
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.41,0:00:28.74,Songs,,0000,0000,0000,,♪Lullaby of Birdland♪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.74,0:00:33.31,Songs,,0000,0000,0000,,Kick my heels going down the slope
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.22,0:00:36.73,Songs,,0000,0000,0000,,As my worthless shadow grows　
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.73,0:00:41.84,Songs,,0000,0000,0000,,It's like an endless summer vacation
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.84,0:00:47.54,Songs,,0000,0000,0000,,Feels like sneakin' into the swimming pool
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.54,0:00:53.60,Songs,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, let's swim with our clothes on, jump in!!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.60,0:00:56.27,Songs,,0000,0000,0000,,A shocking seductive spiral
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.27,0:01:00.77,Songs,,0000,0000,0000,,This beat that pierces my heart is strange　
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.00,0:01:04.18,Songs,,0000,0000,0000,,(It flares up, then vanishes)　
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.18,0:01:06.37,Songs,,0000,0000,0000,,Every miserable day is swell,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.37,0:01:07.31,Songs,,0000,0000,0000,,dress it up
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.31,0:01:10.90,Songs,,0000,0000,0000,,A high-speed swing surrounds us
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.96,0:01:14.88,Songs,,0000,0000,0000,,(What's this dance called? I can't stop)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.88,0:01:18.96,Songs,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you go, it's twined around my ears
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.96,0:01:24.14,Songs,,0000,0000,0000,,and won't leave me ever again
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.30,0:01:27.42,Songs,,0000,0000,0000,,This melody...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.82,0:01:32.90,Songs,,0000,0000,0000,,...is like love
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.32,0:01:54.46,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you going this \Nearly in the morning?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.30,0:01:58.58,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you were acting odd last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.58,0:02:01.31,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like the sneaking \Nsuspicion I had was spot on.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.76,0:02:06.64,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.38,0:02:15.69,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, I said!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.16,0:02:19.31,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Let... go of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.94,0:02:31.04,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Move!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.34,0:02:31.85,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not moving, you idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.71,0:02:35.91,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,If I do, you mean to go \Naway for good, don't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.91,0:02:37.95,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to run off somewhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.43,0:02:41.90,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Are you planning on leaving \Neveryone and everything behind?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.52,0:02:48.98,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry. I can't be here anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.79,0:02:54.35,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Since when did you become such a coward?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.91,0:03:00.20,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Where's the guy that told me "nothing \Ngood comes out of being afraid"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.05,0:03:05.66,Main Dialog,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell are you guys doing \Nthis early in the morning?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.59,0:03:09.76,Main Dialog,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Richie-rich... Are you okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.46,0:03:12.90,Main Dialog,Kota,0000,0000,0000,,Bro?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.37,0:03:19.97,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,So you two were fighting about the festival?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.97,0:03:22.13,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,I understand that you're \Nreally into it, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.81,0:03:26.25,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't sleep last night...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.33,0:03:29.71,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,The truth is I was scared, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.14,0:03:33.61,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.98,0:03:38.35,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Let me stay like this... just for a minute...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.42,0:03:44.30,Main Dialog,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Ritsuko! Did you bring in today's paper?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.37,0:03:48.62,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! I left it by the phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.62,0:03:50.37,Main Dialog,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I see it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.68,0:04:02.39,Main Dialog,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.32,0:04:04.21,Main Dialog,Kota,0000,0000,0000,,It's Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.21,0:04:05.70,Main Dialog,Taichi,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome home, Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.70,0:04:06.40,Main Dialog,Sachiko,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome home!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.40,0:04:07.64,Main Dialog,Taichi,0000,0000,0000,,Did you bring us anything?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.67,0:04:11.02,Main Dialog,Kota,0000,0000,0000,,Dad, your hair's turned gray!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.02,0:04:13.44,Main Dialog,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Has it? I suppose it has...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.44,0:04:15.14,Main Dialog,Taichi,0000,0000,0000,,Did you bring presents?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.50,0:04:16.54,Main Dialog,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I bought you stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.54,0:04:17.42,Main Dialog,Taichi,0000,0000,0000,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.65,0:04:18.17,Main Dialog,Kota,0000,0000,0000,,Let's have 'em!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.17,0:04:21.29,Main Dialog,Sachiko,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, at least let him set \Nfoot in the house first...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.07,0:04:25.41,Caption Top,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome Home, Dad
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.70,0:04:28.29,Main Dialog,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, I'm sorry for \Nbeing away all this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.88,0:04:31.25,Main Dialog,Sachiko,0000,0000,0000,,You look cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.49,0:04:33.20,Main Dialog,Taichi,0000,0000,0000,,Look, Bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.20,0:04:35.00,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,That's great, Taichi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.00,0:04:36.13,Main Dialog,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,And this...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.63,0:04:40.01,Main Dialog,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,...is for you, Sentaro.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.78,0:04:47.29,Main Dialog,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Um... I don't know if you'll \Nlike it or not, though...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.93,0:04:57.40,Main Dialog,Kota,0000,0000,0000,,It's a fountain pen!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.66,0:04:59.12,Main Dialog,Kota,0000,0000,0000,,You're lucky, Bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.12,0:05:00.79,Main Dialog,Taichi,0000,0000,0000,,Wow...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.79,0:05:03.91,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Something expensive like \Nthis is wasted on me...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.55,0:05:08.91,Main Dialog,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,A child doesn't go turning down \Na present from his parent.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.58,0:05:15.25,Main Dialog,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, looks like everyone got a present.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.25,0:05:17.23,Main Dialog,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Sachiko, pass these out.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.23,0:05:18.03,Main Dialog,Sachiko,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.19,0:05:27.84,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,A child... His parent...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.88,0:05:46.61,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Are you coming to practice today?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.71,0:05:51.34,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Startin' today, I'm gonna \Npractice my ass off for the festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.34,0:05:52.51,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,You mean it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.51,0:05:53.29,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,I mean it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.74,0:05:57.44,Main Dialog,Man,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell? That was a weird \Nway to greet to each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.67,0:06:01.92,Caption Top,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Mukae
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.17,0:06:01.92,Main Dialog,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Me, at the festival?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.17,0:06:06.24,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I was hoping that you \Nwould play bass for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.24,0:06:09.40,Main Dialog,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,You're asking me out of the blue...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.40,0:06:11.93,Main Dialog,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Adults have a lot of things \Non their plate, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.93,0:06:13.88,Main Dialog,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,And there'd be so much to prepare...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.28,0:06:15.35,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,You can't do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.15,0:06:28.57,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,You're totally prepared!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.57,0:06:31.12,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Ain't no way we can lose now!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.59,0:06:48.84,Main Dialog,Seiji,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.84,0:06:50.85,Main Dialog,Seiji,0000,0000,0000,,How's it goin' for you guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.76,0:06:52.76,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.76,0:06:55.68,Main Dialog,Seiji,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, we're in the middle \Nof getting our costumes fitted.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.16,0:06:59.81,Main Dialog,Seiji,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way we're going to \Nlose against you guys this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.38,0:07:02.66,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,It's so flamboyant...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.66,0:07:04.32,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,We, on the other hand...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.75,0:07:09.14,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,...are plain. Way too plain...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.25,0:07:12.55,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,We don't have any razzmatazz.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.55,0:07:15.41,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,At this rate, we might not \Nbe able to beat them...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.41,0:07:17.84,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,That stuff doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.84,0:07:20.67,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,All we gotta do is put our music \Nface-to-face against theirs.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.67,0:07:23.49,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I know! I know that...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.75,0:07:27.86,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,...but this is our last school festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.21,0:07:30.50,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I just don't want to have any regrets...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.27,0:07:33.51,Main Dialog,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Easy to say...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.51,0:07:37.79,Main Dialog,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,But appealing to people who have no \Ninterest in jazz is a tall order.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.28,0:07:48.40,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,W-What are you saying?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.40,0:07:50.67,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,I can't sing!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.67,0:07:54.33,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. There are still ten \Ndays left. We'll work it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.61,0:07:58.04,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Ri'ko, if you're gonna \Nrefuse, now's the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.04,0:08:00.73,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,'Cause if you decide to do it, \Nwe're not gonna go easy on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.03,0:08:04.05,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,You don't wanna sing, tell \Nus to shove off right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.86,0:08:09.71,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Though I hope you don't turn us down...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.71,0:08:11.56,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I agree with Sen.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.56,0:08:14.10,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Would you help us out?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.66,0:08:20.80,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Alright. I'll give it a try.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.28,0:08:36.18,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Raindrops on roses and whiskers on kittens...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.95,0:08:46.30,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Raindrops on roses and whiskers on kittens...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.10,0:08:48.59,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Kit-tens...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.98,0:08:51.20,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,No, you've got no swing!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.39,0:08:58.18,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Raindrops on roses and whiskers on kittens
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.18,0:09:01.85,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Bright copper kettles and warm woolen mittens
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.85,0:09:05.67,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Brown paper packages tied up with strings
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.67,0:09:09.19,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,These are a few of my favorite things
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.19,0:09:13.03,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Cream colored ponies and crisp apple strudels
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.03,0:09:16.70,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Doorbells and sleigh bells \Nand schnitzel with noodles
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.70,0:09:20.29,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Wild geese that fly with \Nthe moon on their wings
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.29,0:09:23.92,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,These are a few of my favorite things
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.92,0:09:27.63,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Girls in white dresses with blue satin sashes
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.63,0:09:31.30,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Snowflakes that stay on my nose and eyelashes
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.30,0:09:35.02,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Silver white winters that melt into springs
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.02,0:09:38.84,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,These are a few of my favorite things
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.21,0:09:48.89,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,I simply remember my favorite things
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.89,0:09:56.20,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,And then I don't feel so bad
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.64,0:10:03.02,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,"My Favorite Things"...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.85,0:10:06.19,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,My {\i1}own{\i0} favorite things are...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.19,0:10:09.25,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,The footsteps of a certain person \Nheading towards the house...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.74,0:10:13.35,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,The sound of the piano and drums \Nriffing in the basement...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.35,0:10:15.90,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,The laughter of two boys...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.63,0:10:18.86,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Silly, I know...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.81,0:10:25.06,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Drums and watermelon and onigiri...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.06,0:10:28.73,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Those are a few of my favorite things...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.73,0:10:31.77,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck is that, Sentaro?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.09,0:10:33.74,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Go on, Richie. Your turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.69,0:10:37.06,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Tell us your "favorite things".
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.06,0:10:38.95,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have any!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.35,0:10:43.11,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Even before Ri-chan said hers, \NI had something in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.98,0:10:48.42,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,My "favorite thing" is \Nthis time... right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.88,0:11:01.68,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Tomorrow's the day...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.68,0:11:04.53,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,All that's left is playing \Nour best at the festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.53,0:11:07.98,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Richie... How about playin' \N"Moanin'" one more time?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.98,0:11:11.69,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm... Nah, let's save it for tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.69,0:11:14.55,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,If we started jamming now, we wouldn't stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.28,0:11:16.86,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,I see. Yeah, you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.23,0:11:19.51,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Well, see you tomorrow then. Don't be late.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.51,0:11:20.27,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.69,0:11:30.42,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,He forget to take this...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.96,0:11:34.04,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, well, you don't need a score for jazz.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.31,0:11:35.96,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,An' I can just give it to him tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.79,0:11:42.55,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Oh. Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.55,0:11:45.31,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna run to deliver \Nsomething he left behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.31,0:11:47.85,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Kaoru-san left a while ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.85,0:11:49.42,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,You might not be able to catch up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.42,0:11:51.29,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,I know, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.05,0:12:19.84,Caption Top,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,19th School Festival
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.12,0:12:23.10,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Sen's late...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.10,0:12:24.22,Main Dialog,Seiji,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.22,0:12:26.61,Main Dialog,Seiji,0000,0000,0000,,It's almost time for our battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.61,0:12:29.68,Main Dialog,Seiji,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Where's your partner? \NDon't tell me he's late?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.11,0:12:31.90,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,No, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.22,0:12:34.15,Main Dialog,Yamaoka,0000,0000,0000,,Seiji, come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.15,0:12:36.52,Main Dialog,Seiji,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! Well, see you later!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.20,0:12:44.07,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Ri-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.61,0:12:50.09,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Sentaro...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.39,0:12:54.43,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,He got into an accident on \Na motorbike last night...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.43,0:12:56.36,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,...and was taken to the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.19,0:13:01.76,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,S-So... how is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.76,0:13:04.30,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know! What should I do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.30,0:13:05.08,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Kaoru-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.08,0:13:07.64,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Sentaro is... Sentaro is...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.64,0:13:12.14,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Ri-chan, calm down! I'll go to \Nthe hospital to see how he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.48,0:13:14.62,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Stay here until I get back.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.82,0:13:21.23,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.23,0:13:25.82,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I've dashed down this slope countless \Ntimes, but it's never felt this long...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.95,0:13:30.20,Caption Top,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,City Hospital
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.83,0:13:30.20,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Um, excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.20,0:13:31.06,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I'm looking for...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.06,0:13:34.15,Main Dialog,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,I'll help you when it's your \Nturn, so please get in line.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.70,0:13:36.84,Main Dialog,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.01,0:13:51.81,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,U-Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.24,0:13:55.02,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I heard there was an accident...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.02,0:14:00.02,Main Dialog,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,They've finished operating... \Nbut it's serious head trauma...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.73,0:14:03.32,Main Dialog,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Still hasn't regained consciousness...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.74,0:14:09.28,Caption Top,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,No Visitors
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.74,0:14:09.28,Main Dialog,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Might never wake up again... \Nthe doctor said...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.28,0:14:11.16,Main Dialog,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Don't talk like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.83,0:14:13.30,Main Dialog,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.07,0:14:20.26,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,That's right! Even when Sen is all bloody \Nfrom a fight, he just laughs it off!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.81,0:14:27.42,Main Dialog,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Um... Sachiko is the one who's in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.81,0:14:35.89,Main Dialog,Kota,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know why... but Sis was riding on \Nthe back of Bro's motorbike last night...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.15,0:14:38.49,Main Dialog,Kota,0000,0000,0000,,They got hit by a car...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.56,0:14:42.40,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Then how is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.40,0:14:45.21,Main Dialog,Kota,0000,0000,0000,,He's hurt, but not too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.69,0:14:48.47,Main Dialog,Kota,0000,0000,0000,,He was sitting over here just before...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.47,0:14:50.34,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I see. Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.13,0:14:59.58,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,That's right! The place he's \Nmost likely to go is...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.58,0:15:00.88,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Gotta be...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.23,0:16:07.27,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,I've seen this angel before somewhere...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.89,0:16:15.10,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,If you're gonna take somebody to Heaven, \Ncould you make it me an' not Sachiko, angel?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.39,0:16:26.32,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Why do I end up hurting the \Nones I most want to protect?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.13,0:16:34.48,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Why... was I even born?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.29,0:16:42.60,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Richie? What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.11,0:16:45.61,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Hey... What are you cryin' for?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.45,0:16:54.99,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,This way, we don't have \Nto see each other cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.35,0:16:59.35,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean "we"? I ain't...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.35,0:17:01.06,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay to cry, Sen.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.65,0:17:05.96,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,You've been keeping it \Nbottled up all this time...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.81,0:17:47.88,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Sa-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.88,0:17:50.13,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.37,0:17:53.18,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Sen...?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.37,0:18:06.11,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,At the time, it looked like \Nhe was just stepping out...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.70,0:18:12.93,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,...but he disappeared, and the festival \Nwas over before it even began.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.57,0:18:14.40,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,And then...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.40,0:18:17.78,Main Dialog,Sachiko,0000,0000,0000,,Richie...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.09,0:18:19.34,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Kaoru-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.47,0:18:24.41,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Um, here. If you're able to eat these...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.92,0:18:27.54,Main Dialog,Sachiko,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know where my big bro, Sen went?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.95,0:18:33.75,Main Dialog,Sachiko,0000,0000,0000,,He would normally never \Ngive me a ride on his bike.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.75,0:18:40.05,Main Dialog,Sachiko,0000,0000,0000,,But I had a twisted ankle and \Nkept complaining about it to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.15,0:18:43.43,Main Dialog,Sachiko,0000,0000,0000,,The accident was my fault...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.05,0:18:46.67,Main Dialog,Sachiko,0000,0000,0000,,I have to apologize to him...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.94,0:18:54.32,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Sa-chan, right now, if you focus on getting \Nbetter, Sentaro will come back soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.32,0:18:56.92,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,You want to show him that \Nyou're healthy again, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.80,0:18:58.71,Main Dialog,Sachiko,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.16,0:19:08.69,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,I said all that to Sa-chan, \Nbut the truth is...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.06,0:19:15.17,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Kaoru-san, what'll I do if \NSentaro never comes back?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.78,0:19:17.68,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Ri-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.16,0:19:19.89,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,We're talking about him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.89,0:19:23.76,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I bet when we least expect \Nit, he'll suddenly turn up.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.76,0:19:25.52,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you have that feeling?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.69,0:19:31.60,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. You're right. He \Nwill come back, won't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.60,0:19:32.33,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.42,0:19:36.65,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Kaoru-san... Don't go anywhere, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.80,0:19:42.66,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.66,0:19:43.93,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.12,0:19:48.58,Main Dialog,Priest,0000,0000,0000,,Oh. I remember you. Richie-kun, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.84,0:19:51.72,Main Dialog,Priest,0000,0000,0000,,Do {\i1}I{\i0} know where he might be?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.09,0:19:55.12,Main Dialog,Priest,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm afraid I don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.66,0:20:00.86,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Um... Father, he left this behind...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.34,0:20:08.89,Main Dialog,Priest,0000,0000,0000,,He once told me the reason he always wore \Nthe rosary as a necklace was because
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.89,0:20:16.33,Main Dialog,Priest,0000,0000,0000,,he was afraid that if he lost it, he \Nwould be abandoned by the world...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.55,0:20:42.60,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Se...!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.05,0:20:52.07,Main Dialog,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,I thought maybe Sen had come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.08,0:21:01.45,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Pops... He's not coming back.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.14,0:21:06.51,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I'll never be able to \Npractice with him again.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.51,0:21:09.61,Main Dialog,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,W-What are you talkin' about, Richie?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.96,0:21:13.58,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Never again...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.84,0:21:28.64,Songs,,0000,0000,0000,,I waited for you on that slope　
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.56,0:21:36.92,Songs,,0000,0000,0000,,For our after school promise　
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.92,0:21:41.91,Songs,,0000,0000,0000,,There was a 'goodbye' blurred far away　
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.87,0:21:56.22,Songs,,0000,0000,0000,,I was so weak, so awkward, and so fragile back then
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.22,0:22:03.77,Songs,,0000,0000,0000,,But you gave me a small pair of wings　         　　
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.13,0:22:09.83,Songs,,0000,0000,0000,,In the twilight hour of the sky,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.83,0:22:15.48,Songs,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm searching for a gleam of light　　　　　　　
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.48,0:22:23.45,Songs,,0000,0000,0000,,If only I could have said that I love you…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.96,0:22:35.72,Songs,,0000,0000,0000,,The note that I wrote in the corner of my textbook
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.61,0:22:48.80,Songs,,0000,0000,0000,,has never been delivered to this day
